{"tid":851080,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【本港樓市】二手樓價指數連跌五周，下旬有較全面調整訊號","createTime":"2018-10-07T01:03:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T02:25:39.000Z","uid":162303,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5f69540602f35bf88c7a3bf792096df0bddab0e7","tid":851080,"uid":162303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T01:03:03.000Z","msg":"《經濟通通訊社５日專訊》中原地產研究部高級聯席董事黃良昇指出，近四周計，四大整體<br />\n指數齊跌，四周內出現三次，樓價走勢反覆回軟。當中ＣＣＬ（中小型單位）連跌５周共<br />\n１﹒５２％，回軟走勢較明顯。甫踏入第四季，整體樓價有望出現較全面的調整訊號，將會在<br />\n１０月下旬公布的ＣＣＬ開始反映。<br />\n　　中原城市領先指數ＣＣＬ最新報１８５﹒５１點，按周跌０﹒５８％。中原城市大型屋苑領<br />\n先指數ＣＣＬＭａｓｓ報１８８﹒５９點，按周跌０﹒１８％。ＣＣＬ（中小型單位）報<br />\n１８６﹒３１點，按周跌０﹒３５％。ＣＣＬ（大型單位）報１８１﹒３３點，按周跌<br />\n１﹒８４％。當中ＣＣＬ、ＣＣＬ＿Ｍａｓｓ及ＣＣＬ（大型單位）於四周內同樣一升三跌，分<br />\n別累跌１﹒５６％、１﹒２８％及２﹒０４％。（ｃｙ）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76c74fb50460525795c6650d7dbc92ceec145e5d","tid":851080,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T01:05:27.000Z","msg":"嘩跌好撚多呀好撚驚驚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6260c7899fef36c673bc0baa466288e9979d902","tid":851080,"uid":162526,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T02:15:31.000Z","msg":"假跌唔計"},{"pid":"0bfc11e2d4b11ff03ca8a3c7e82f1e6ec13d4c58","tid":851080,"uid":159798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T02:25:39.000Z","msg":"「較全面的調整訊號」即係點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}